Preamble: My TENT Mission 3. 0 has announced the procedure for the award of cash prizes to the winning local bodies in 119 categories and the appropriation of this prize money vide Government Decision dated 5th June, 2023 at Reference No. (1). Accordingly, a Detailed Project Report of the works to be taken up by the local bodies out of the award amount has been prepared vide Government Decision dated 08.02.2022 at Reference No. Administrative approval has to be obtained from a committee constituted under the chairmanship of Secretary, Department of Environment and Climate Change.

2. Accordingly, for grant of administrative approval to the Detailed Project Report received from the Awardee Local Bodies, Ms. The Committee has made recommendations after discussing the Detailed Project Report submitted by the Local Bodies in its meetings held on 02.05.2025 under the Chairmanship of Secretary, Department of Environment & Climate Change. It was under the consideration of the government to grant administrative approval to the Detailed Project Report of the respective local bodies as recommended by the committee.

Government Decision: Considering the points mentioned in the Preamble, the total amount of Rs. The works to be taken up out of the prize money of Rs. The detailed project report of the cost of 1,50,71, 494.50 (Rupees one crore fifty lakhs seventy one thousand four hundred and ninety four and fifty paise only) has been submitted by the Principal, Akole Nagar Panchayat with the technical approval of the City Magistrate, Ahilyanagar Municipal Corporation. The proposal was submitted by the Akole Nagar Panchayat.

As per the recommendation made by the said committee, the total amount submitted by Akole Nagar Panchayat is Rs. The works in the Detailed Project Report costing 1,50,71, 494.50 (Rupees one crore fifty lakhs seventy one thousand four hundred and ninety four rupees fifty only) are being accorded administrative sanction by the Government subject to the following conditions and conditions. The works for which administrative sanction is being granted are shown in the accompanying Annexure-9.
2. Terms and Conditions 1) The working mechanism for the works in this Detailed Project Report shall be in Akole Nagar Panchayat.

(2) The detailed project report shall be sent to my Vasundhara Mission Directorate by the 5th of every month, along with the physical progress report of the implementation of the works mentioned in this Detailed Project Report.
3) The implementation of the works in this Detailed Project Report should be completed within the next 6 months from the approval of the Administrator.
4) If the amount of the prize exceeds the amount, it should be made out of self-funding.
5) In case of any increase in the original project cost in this Detailed Project Report for any reason, no additional funds / grants will be made available for the same.
